name: An Odd Portrait of Self Growth
description:
A look back on a year of creating,
each corner of this portrait takes the
eye on a dance across different
pieces of time in the development of a
young artist. "I was looking forward
and not inward. I was looking
backward but not upwards." | 8000 x
9600 | Collector of this piece will
receive a high-quality metal print as
well as an accompanying painting
